<font color="yellow">Jadi, tidak ada seorang pun dari keluargamu yang akan menuntutku, kan?</font>

178
00:11:21,940 --> 00:11:23,110
<font color="yellow">Tunggu, lepaskan!</font>

179
00:11:24,250 --> 00:11:25,850
<font color="yellow">Berhenti di sana!</font>

180
00:11:48,010 --> 00:11:50,000
<font color="yellow">Ini favoritku!</font>

181
00:11:50,730 --> 00:11:52,970
<font color="yellow">Kau tahu kue ini? Di pinggir jalan?</font>

182
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,730
<font color="yellow">Ya! Aku menyukainya.</font>

183
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:55,380
<font color="yellow">Sungguh?</font>

184
00:11:55,450 --> 00:11:58,830
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu, apa kau tahu juga kedai mie di pinggir jalan sana?</font>

185
00:11:59,570 --> 00:12:02,080
<font color="yellow">Sup mereka luar biasa!</font>

186
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:05,360
<font color="yellow">Aku juga menyukainya!
