188
00:12:09,410 --> 00:12:10,910
<font color="yellow">Supnya sangat terasa!</font>

189
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:13,210
<font color="yellow">Mie-nya juga memiliki tekstur yang bagus!</font>

190
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,520
<font color="yellow">Oh, maaf.</font>

191
00:12:15,620 --> 00:12:17,070
<font color="yellow">Aku jadi kemana-mana.</font>

192
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:20,650
<font color="yellow">Tidak masalah, kok!
Aku selalu suka membicarakan tentang tempat makanan lezat!</font>

193
00:12:21,060 --> 00:12:24,000
<font color="yellow">Tapi, dengan siapa kau biasanya pergi makan?</font>

194
00:12:24,890 --> 00:12:25,590
<font color="yellow">Pacar?</font>

195
00:12:25,610 --> 00:12:27,140
<font color="yellow">Tidak!</font>

196
00:12:27,170 --> 00:12:28,770
<font color="yellow">- Joo-ri.
- Joo-ri?</font>

197
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:34,410
<font color="yellow">Ah, Lee Joo-ri, teman sekelasmu?</font>

198
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:35,310
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

199
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:38,420
<font color="yellow">Dia temanku,
tapi dia di level berbeda.</font>

200
00:12:38,740 --> 00:12:41,440
<font color="yellow">Dia sangat tegar,
jadi dia bisa bertahan dalam situasi apa pun.</font>

201
00:12:41,450 --> 00:12:42,930
<font color="yellow">Dia juga sangat sensitif.</font>

202
00:12:43,310 --> 00:12:46,650
<font color="yellow">Kau pasti bersahabat dekat dengan dia.
Kau begitu menghargai dia.</font>

203
00:12:46,910 --> 00:12:48,770
<font color="yellow">Dia lebih baik lagi padaku.</font>

204
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:53,930
<font color="yellow">Sekarang, aku akan menanyakan beberapa pertanyaan formal yang tidak biasa.</font>

205
00:12:54,260 --> 00:12:54,910
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

206
00:13:05,350 --> 00:13:07,730
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kau katakan padanya?
Tidak ada kesalahan, kan?</font>

207
00:13:07,770 --> 00:13:09,450
<font color="yellow">Katakan padaku semua yang kau ingat!</font>

208
00:13:10,450 --> 00:13:13,950
<font color="yellow">Kau tidak perlu kuatir, Joo-ri.
Detektif itu sangat baik!</font>

209
00:13:14,220 --> 00:13:15,350
<font color="yellow">Detektif?</font>

210
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:17,870
<font color="yellow">Tidak mungkin!</font>

211
00:13:18,070 --> 00:13:19,870
<font color="yellow">Apa dia detektif penanggung-jawab kasus Lee So-woo?</font>

212
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:22,630
<font color="yellow">Yang datang saat mayatnya ditemukan?</font>

213
00:13:24,180 --> 00:13:26,590
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak yakin.
Aku kurang pintar mengingat wajah orang.</font>

214
00:13:27,590 --> 00:13:29,110
<font color="yellow">Jadi, apa sebenarnya yang bisa kau lakukan?</font>

215
00:13:29,140 --> 00:13:30,740
<font color="yellow">Joo-ri?</font>

216
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,320
<font color="yellow">Kau selanjutnya.</font>

217
00:13:34,380 --> 00:13:36,050
<font color="yellow">Ya, aku akan segera ke sana.</font>

218
00:13:40,950 --> 00:13:43,060
<font color="yellow">Kau banyak memikirkan tentang Lee So-woo?</font>

219
00:13:43,070 --> 00:13:44,570
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

220
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,920
<font color="yellow">Mungkin karena insiden itu tidak wajar.</font>

221
00:13:47,020 --> 00:13:49,890
<font color="yellow">Aku mengalami masa sulit karena terus memikirkan hal itu
meski aku juga tidak menginginkannya.</font>

222
00:13:50,950 --> 00:13:55,670
<font color="yellow">Aku merasa lega saat mendengar bahwa konseling psikologis akan diberikan.</font>

223
00:13:55,880 --> 00:14:00,270
<font color="yellow">Insiden tidak wajar? Dari segi apa?</font>

224
00:14:02,420 --> 00:14:04,220
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak tahu juga.</font>

225
00:14:05,050 --> 00:14:06,650
<font color="yellow">Hanya saja aku merasa seperti itu.</font>

226
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:12,080
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak terlalu dekat dengan dia,
tapi dia terlihat seperti orang yang baik dan peduli.</font>

227
00:14:12,900 --> 00:14:14,970
<font color="yellow">Kudengar, dia tidak meninggalkan surat perpisahan?</font>

228
00:14:16,070 --> 00:14:19,340
<font color="yellow">Tidak masuk akal seseorang seperti So-woo
akan bunuh diri...</font>

229
00:14:19,350 --> 00:14:21,220
<font color="yellow">tanpa alasan, tanpa pesan apa pun.</font>

230
00:14:21,860 --> 00:14:22,910
<font color="yellow">Benar, kan?</font>

231
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:25,870
<font color="yellow">Memang harus bagaimana supaya insiden itu dianggap wajar?</font>

232
00:14:27,170 --> 00:14:28,660
<font color="yellow">Dia kepeleset, begitu?</font>

233
00:14:28,730 --> 00:14:30,530
<font color="yellow">Atau... seseorang mendorong dia sampai jatuh?</font>

234
00:14:31,190 --> 00:14:32,790
<font color="yellow">Entahlah.</font>

235
00:14:33,060 --> 00:14:36,710
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak berpikir sejauh itu, sih.</font>

236
00:14:36,770 --> 00:14:38,700
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana menurutmu, Detektif?</font>

237
00:14:39,180 --> 00:14:42,190
<font color="yellow">Aku di sini sebagai konselor, bukan polisi.</font>

238
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:44,310
<font color="yellow">Tugasku di sini hanya mendengarkan kalian.</font>

239
00:14:44,860 --> 00:14:46,050
<font color="yellow">Benarkah?</font>

240
00:14:46,930 --> 00:14:49,930
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu... kenapa kau datang sendirian?</font>

241
00:14:50,270 --> 00:14:52,290
<font color="yellow">Sekolah juga merekrut konselor, kok.</font>

242
00:14:52,950 --> 00:14:55,010
<font color="yellow">Konseling bukanlah tugas polisi.</font>

243
00:15:04,340 --> 00:15:05,940
<font color="yellow">Kalau sudah selesai, aku mau pergi.</font>

244
00:15:05,970 --> 00:15:07,570
<font color="yellow">Ah, sebentar.</font>

245
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:09,870
<font color="yellow">Aku melupakan pertanyaan ini.</font>

246
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:13,910
<font color="yellow">Apakah ada hal lain yang kau ingat soal So-woo?</font>

247
00:15:13,940 --> 00:15:16,150
<font color="yellow">Siapa yang dekat dengan So-woo, atau...</font>

248
00:15:16,190 --> 00:15:19,120
<font color="yellow">- ...yang tidak akur dengan dia?
- Aku tidak tahu apa-apa!</font>

249
00:15:19,350 --> 00:15:22,240
<font color="yellow">Karena aku tidak terlalu peduli pada murid lain.</font>

250
00:15:24,040 --> 00:15:26,640
<font color="yellow">Baiklah. Kerja bagus. Sampai jumpa lain waktu.</font>

251
00:15:26,710 --> 00:15:28,310
<font color="yellow">Baik</font>

252
00:15:38,040 --> 00:15:40,200
<font color="yellow">Ayo ke rumahku dan makan sesuatu yang lezat!</font>

253
00:15:40,650 --> 00:15:41,280
<font color="yellow">Oke.</font>

254
00:15:46,810 --> 00:15:48,110
<font color="yellow">Hei!</font>

255
00:15:48,340 --> 00:15:49,820
<font color="yellow">Kalian berdua!</font>

256
00:15:49,990 --> 00:15:51,920
<font color="yellow">Lihat siapa di sini!</font>

257
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:56,100
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kalian selalu berdua?
Kalian tidak capek selalu bersama?</font>

258
00:15:56,110 --> 00:15:58,510
<font color="yellow">- Wow, itu membuatku takut.
- Menakutkan sekali!</font>

259
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:03,060
<font color="yellow">- Matamu mungkin akan meloncat keluar.
- Aku benar-benar merasa takut!</font>

260
00:16:03,770 --> 00:16:04,700
<font color="yellow">Lihat apa kau?</font>

261
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,910
<font color="yellow">Joo-ri, ayo pergi.</font>

262
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:09,650
<font color="yellow">Kau lihat apa, huh?</font>

263
00:16:29,670 --> 00:16:30,610
<font color="yellow">Oh, tidak!</font>

264
00:16:30,660 --> 00:16:32,450
<font color="yellow">Lukanya akan membekas!</font>

265
00:16:33,130 --> 00:16:36,520
<font color="yellow">Sedikit bekas luka tidak masalah.
Toh kau selalu kelihatan kotor.</font>

266
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:39,770
<font color="yellow">Ayo pergi. Dia bau.</font>

267
00:17:01,760 --> 00:17:03,360
<font color="yellow">Mereka jahat sekali.</font>

268
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:22,940
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih.</font>

269
00:17:22,970 --> 00:17:24,700
<font color="yellow">Kalian murid SMA Jeong-guk?</font>

270
00:17:24,740 --> 00:17:26,340
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

271
00:17:26,490 --> 00:17:28,450
<font color="yellow">Tapi... siapa kau?</font>

272
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:49,360
<font color="yellow">(Lee Joo-ri, Park Cho-rong -> Harus bertemu mereka lagi,
kemungkinannya tinggi)</font>

273
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:56,460
<font color="yellow">Hei!</font>

274
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:58,920
<font color="yellow">Murid tidak diijinkan masuk kemari.</font>

275
00:17:59,040 --> 00:18:00,810
<font color="yellow">Guruku mengirimku untuk memberikan ini.</font>

276
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:02,490
<font color="yellow">Ucapkan terima kasih padanya.</font>

277
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:03,160
<font color="yellow">Baik.</font>

278
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:05,810
<font color="yellow">Sampai jumpa lagi.</font>

279
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:07,560
<font color="yellow">Oh, Seo-yeon!</font>

280
00:18:08,460 --> 00:18:09,950
<font color="yellow">Kau tidak melihat ini, kan?</font>

281
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:12,710
<font color="yellow">Tidaklah!</font>

282
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,490
<font color="yellow">Oke. Pergilah.</font>

283
00:18:15,170 --> 00:18:16,770
<font color="yellow">Sampai jumpa.</font>

284
00:18:23,090 --> 00:18:24,690
<font color="yellow">Lee Joo-ri?</font>

285
00:18:25,020 --> 00:18:26,620
<font color="yellow">Park Cho-rong?</font>

286
00:18:39,950 --> 00:18:41,550
<font color="yellow">Cho-rong!</font>

287
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:43,680
<font color="yellow">Kau punya waktu?</font>

288
00:18:48,120 --> 00:18:52,790
<font color="yellow">- Aku baru akan mengambilkannya!
- Tidak perlu, kurasa aku yang paling kuat di sini.</font>

289
00:18:55,560 --> 00:18:57,160
<font color="yellow">Ini...</font>

290
00:18:58,180 --> 00:18:59,780
<font color="yellow">Kurasa, kau meninggalkan ini.</font>

291
00:19:00,660 --> 00:19:02,790
<font color="yellow">Tidak, aku belum pernah melihatnya.</font>

292
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:04,230
<font color="yellow">Benarkah?</font>

293
00:19:04,260 --> 00:19:05,860
<font color="yellow">Ini ada di mejamu.</font>

294
00:19:06,240 --> 00:19:08,840
<font color="yellow">Kurasa milik orang lain, maaf.</font>

295
00:19:10,340 --> 00:19:12,720
<font color="yellow">Ini pertama kalinya kita bertiga jalan bersama.</font>

296
00:19:12,800 --> 00:19:14,400
<font color="yellow">Mari kita bicara!</font>

297
00:19:15,890 --> 00:19:16,830
<font color="yellow">Oke!</font>

298
00:19:17,770 --> 00:19:18,950
<font color="yellow">Oh, benar.</font>

299
00:19:19,430 --> 00:19:21,800
<font color="yellow">Kau ingat restoran yang terakhir kali kau rekomendasikan?</font>

300
00:19:21,840 --> 00:19:23,440
<font color="yellow">Ya, kau sudah mencobanya?</font>

301
00:19:23,590 --> 00:19:24,650
<font color="yellow">Belum.</font>

302
00:19:24,730 --> 00:19:27,870
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah ke sana, sih. Tapi antriannya sampai 3 jam!
