303
00:19:27,980 --> 00:19:30,370
<font color="yellow">Salah juga sih aku ke sana waktu Natal.</font>

304
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:32,010
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kau lakukan saat Natal?</font>

305
00:19:32,020 --> 00:19:32,780
<font color="yellow">Aku?</font>

306
00:19:32,840 --> 00:19:35,080
<font color="yellow">Orang tuaku dan aku makan ayam dari layanan pesan antar.</font>

307
00:19:35,150 --> 00:19:36,720
<font color="yellow">Dan juga daging babi!</font>

308
00:19:36,940 --> 00:19:39,990
<font color="yellow">Tradisi Natal di keluargaku adalah makan apa pun yang kami inginkan!</font>

309
00:19:40,170 --> 00:19:41,980
<font color="yellow">Itu membuatku sangat bahagia!</font>

310
00:19:42,190 --> 00:19:43,790
<font color="yellow">Kedengarannya menyenangkan.</font>

311
00:19:45,230 --> 00:19:46,830
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana denganmu, Joo-ri?</font>

312
00:19:47,130 --> 00:19:49,130
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kau lakukan saat natal?</font>

313
00:19:50,340 --> 00:19:51,870
<font color="yellow">Kau pikir kau cukup dekat denganku?</font>

314
00:19:51,870 --> 00:19:52,440
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

315
00:19:52,570 --> 00:19:55,980
<font color="yellow">Kau kira kita cukup dekat untukmu bisa menginterogasiku?</font>

316
00:19:56,010 --> 00:19:56,870
<font color="yellow">Joo-ri...</font>

317
00:19:56,900 --> 00:19:58,500
<font color="yellow">Interogasi?</font>

318
00:19:58,590 --> 00:19:59,750
<font color="yellow">Kita hanya sedang mengobrol.</font>

319
00:19:59,780 --> 00:20:02,330
<font color="yellow">Tapi biasanya kita tidak pernah melakukannya.</font>

320
00:20:02,970 --> 00:20:07,170
<font color="yellow">Lalu kenapa kau tiba-tiba penasaran dengan yang kulakukan
saat Natal?</font>

321
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:09,590
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak tahu kalau itu topik yang sensitif buatmu.</font>

322
00:20:09,620 --> 00:20:11,220
<font color="yellow">Aku yang salah.</font>

323
00:20:11,370 --> 00:20:13,300
<font color="yellow">Kau adalah murid paling pintar di sekolah!</font>

324
00:20:13,340 --> 00:20:14,940
<font color="yellow">Dan kau bilang itu kesalahan?</font>

325
00:20:16,570 --> 00:20:18,960
<font color="yellow">Maaf karena mengajak kalian bertemu tiba-tiba begini.</font>

326
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:20,580
<font color="yellow">Sampai jumpa di sekolah.</font>

327
00:20:20,710 --> 00:20:23,040
<font color="yellow">Di situlah memang tempatmu.</font>

328
00:20:23,690 --> 00:20:27,370
<font color="yellow">Tempat dimana kau selalu merasa begitu hebat karena
semua murid dan guru memujimu.</font>

329
00:20:27,410 --> 00:20:29,370
<font color="yellow">Kau bukan apa-apa saat di luar sekolah.</font>

330
00:20:29,470 --> 00:20:30,700
<font color="yellow">Lihat dirimu!</font>

331
00:20:30,760 --> 00:20:32,750
<font color="yellow">Kau melarikan diri hanya karena aku mengucapkan beberapa kalimat!</font>

332
00:20:33,040 --> 00:20:34,640
<font color="yellow">Lee Joo-ri.</font>

333
00:20:34,860 --> 00:20:35,650
<font color="yellow">Kalau yang kau maksud soal insiden itu...</font>

334
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:37,280
<font color="yellow">Diam kau!</font>

335
00:20:39,310 --> 00:20:40,800
<font color="yellow">Kita sudah selesai, kan?</font>

336
00:20:42,100 --> 00:20:43,610
<font color="yellow">- Park Cho-rong, ayo pergi.
- Joo-ri...</font>

337
00:20:43,620 --> 00:20:45,350
<font color="yellow">Aku bilang bangun!</font>

338
00:20:51,840 --> 00:20:53,110
<font color="yellow">Joo-ri!</font>

339
00:20:53,260 --> 00:20:56,070
<font color="yellow">Memang aku mengatakan sesuatu yang salah?
Tenanglah...</font>

340
00:20:56,120 --> 00:20:58,110
<font color="yellow">Aku akan menelepon reporter itu.</font>

341
00:20:58,130 --> 00:20:59,050
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

342
00:20:59,060 --> 00:21:01,720
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak tahu yang dia ketahui, tapi...</font>

343
00:21:01,770 --> 00:21:03,480
<font color="yellow">...Ko Seo-yeon mencurigai kita.</font>

344
00:21:03,980 --> 00:21:06,580
<font color="yellow">Aku yakin, dia akan memberitahu semua orang soal itu!</font>

345
00:21:07,050 --> 00:21:08,710
<font color="yellow">Maka, aku harus mengambil langkah lebih dulu.</font>

346
00:21:08,850 --> 00:21:11,300
<font color="yellow">Tapi belum ada yang pasti di sini, mungkin kita bisa...</font>

347
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:12,920
<font color="yellow">Diam!</font>

348
00:21:16,010 --> 00:21:17,260
<font color="yellow">Halo?</font>

349
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:19,850
<font color="yellow">Sebelumnya, aku mendapat kartu namamu.</font>

350
00:21:20,420 --> 00:21:22,020
<font color="yellow">Aku akan melakukan wawancara itu.</font>

351
00:21:22,470 --> 00:21:26,130
<font color="yellow">Kau bilang kalau kau bisa memburamkan wajah dan mengubah suaraku, kan?</font>

352
00:21:26,730 --> 00:21:30,390
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih untuk waktumu,
sampai jumpa besok.</font>

353
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:33,360
<font color="yellow">Bagus!</font>

354
00:21:34,910 --> 00:21:38,080
<font color="yellow">Pak Choi! Pak Choi!</font>

355
00:21:38,870 --> 00:21:41,220
<font color="yellow">Halo! Saya Park Hyun-min, reporter yang Anda jumpai waktu itu.</font>

356
00:21:41,230 --> 00:21:43,360
<font color="yellow">Apakah Anda ingin mengatakan sesuatu tentang kecurigaan
yang mengarah pada putera Anda?</font>

357
00:21:43,620 --> 00:21:46,480
<font color="yellow">Beberapa orang mencurigai putera Anda membunuh Lee So-woo!</font>

358
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:48,210
<font color="yellow">Pak Choi!</font>

359
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:50,440
<font color="yellow">Orang-orang mencurigai Choi Woo-hyuk sebagai pembunuh!</font>

